snippet.title: Entropy : Zero - Uprising - Upcoming Mod of the Year 2022
snippet.description:
In the recent process of ModDB's annual Mod of the Year, Entropy : Zero - Uprising not only scored in the top 100 mods, but was also awarded the best upcoming mod of 2022 on ModDB! Thanks to everyone who voted!

The ModDB upcoming MOTY announcement: https://www.moddb.com/groups/2022-mod-of-the-year-awards/features/players-choice-best-upcoming-mod-2022
Read our latest article here: https://www.moddb.com/mods/entropy-zero-uprising/news/entropy-zero-uprising-best-upcoming-mod-of-the-year-2022
Our ModDB page: https://www.moddb.com/mods/entropy-zero-uprising
